Tendenci 5.0 README
-------------------

XAPIAN REQUIREMENTS (Development Only)
--------------------------------------
Since some fields are faceted in the search indexes so xapian is required.
For Ubuntu:
sudo apt-get install libxapian15
sudo apt-get install python-xapian

OSX/Windows installation instructions are here:
http://xapian.org/download

INSTALLATION
------------
* With virtualenvwrapper:
http://www.doughellmann.com/projects/virtualenvwrapper/

git clone git@github.com:schipul/Tendenci-5.0.git
mkvirtualenv Tendenci50-env
workon Tendenci50-env
source scripts/tendenci-boot.sh

* Without virtualenvwrapper:

git clone git@github.com:schipul/Tendenci-5.0.git
virtualenv Tendenci50-env
source  Tendenci50-env/bin/activate
source scripts/tendenci-boot.sh

SETUP DATABASE AND INDEX
------------------------
From root site folder (eg Tendenci50):
python manage.py syncdb
python manage.py rebuild_index